---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="India IPO Tracker">

  <section class="content-section" style="margin-top:48px">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2 class="section-title">📋 India IPO Tracker</h2>
      <span class="section-live">NSE · BSE</span>
    </div>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:28px">
      Upcoming, ongoing, and recently listed IPOs on Indian exchanges. Data sourced from NSE and refreshes twice daily.
    </p>

    <div class="ipo-tabs">
      <button class="ipo-tab active" id="tabOngoing">Open Now</button>
      <button class="ipo-tab" id="tabUpcoming">Upcoming</button>
      <button class="ipo-tab" id="tabListed">Recently Listed</button>
      <button class="ipo-tab" id="tabGuide">IPO Guide</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Ongoing -->
    <div id="panelOngoing">
      <div class="ec-loading" id="ongoingLoading">Loading open IPOs…</div>
      <div id="ongoingContent" style="display:none"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Upcoming -->
    <div id="panelUpcoming" style="display:none">
      <div class="ec-loading" id="upcomingLoading">Loading upcoming IPOs…</div>
      <div id="upcomingContent" style="display:none"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Listed -->
    <div id="panelListed" style="display:none">
      <div class="ec-loading" id="listedLoading">Loading recently listed IPOs…</div>
      <div id="listedContent" style="display:none"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- IPO Guide -->
    <div id="panelGuide" style="display:none">
      <div class="ipo-guide">
        <h3 class="guide-section-title">How Indian IPOs Work</h3>

        <div class="guide-steps">
          <div class="guide-step">
            <div class="guide-step-num">1</div>
            <div>
              <div class="guide-step-title">DRHP Filing</div>
              <div class="guide-step-desc">Company files Draft Red Herring Prospectus (DRHP) with SEBI. Contains all financial details, risks, and use of funds. SEBI review takes 30–75 days.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-step">
            <div class="guide-step-num">2</div>
            <div>
              <div class="guide-step-title">Price Band Announcement</div>
              <div class="guide-step-desc">Company announces price band (e.g., ₹400–₹420 per share). The upper end is the "cut-off price" you can bid at to maximise allotment chances.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-step">
            <div class="guide-step-num">3</div>
            <div>
              <div class="guide-step-title">Subscription Window (3 days)</div>
              <div class="guide-step-desc">IPO opens for 3 days. You apply via UPI-linked broker (Zerodha, Groww, etc.) or bank ASBA. Minimum lot size is typically 1 lot = ₹14,000–₹15,000.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-step">
            <div class="guide-step-num">4</div>
            <div>
              <div class="guide-step-title">Allotment (T+6)</div>
              <div class="guide-step-desc">If oversubscribed, allotment is by lottery (retail). Money is blocked via UPI/ASBA until allotment. If not allotted, funds are released within 24 hours.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-step">
            <div class="guide-step-num">5</div>
            <div>
              <div class="guide-step-title">Listing Day (T+6)</div>
              <div class="guide-step-desc">Shares credited to your demat account. Stock lists on NSE/BSE. Grey market premium (GMP) gives a hint of listing gains, but it's unofficial and risky to rely on.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-tips-grid">
          <div class="guide-tip">
            <div class="guide-tip-icon">✅</div>
            <div class="guide-tip-title">Apply at Cut-off Price</div>
            <div class="guide-tip-text">Always apply at the upper end of the price band (cut-off) to maximise allotment chances in oversubscribed IPOs.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-tip">
            <div class="guide-tip-icon">⚠️</div>
            <div class="guide-tip-title">GMP ≠ Guaranteed Returns</div>
            <div class="guide-tip-text">Grey Market Premium is unofficial and speculative. Listing price can be very different. Don't FOMO based on GMP alone.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-tip">
            <div class="guide-tip-icon">📊</div>
            <div class="guide-tip-title">Read the DRHP</div>
            <div class="guide-tip-text">Check promoter background, revenue growth over 3 years, debt levels, and "Use of Proceeds" — fresh issue vs. OFS matters a lot.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="guide-tip">
            <div class="guide-tip-icon">🏦</div>
            <div class="guide-tip-title">Fresh Issue vs. OFS</div>
            <div class="guide-tip-text">Fresh Issue = money goes to the company for growth. OFS (Offer for Sale) = existing shareholders cashing out. Prefer IPOs with higher fresh issue portion.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-quota" style="margin-top:24px">
          <div class="guide-quota-title">Who gets what? IPO Quota Breakdown</div>
          <div class="guide-quota-grid">
            <div class="guide-quota-item">
              <div class="guide-quota-pct" style="color:#3b82f6">50%</div>
              <div class="guide-quota-lbl">QIB</div>
              <div class="guide-quota-desc">Qualified Institutional Buyers (mutual funds, banks, FIIs)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="guide-quota-item">
              <div class="guide-quota-pct" style="color:#f59e0b">15%</div>
              <div class="guide-quota-lbl">NII / HNI</div>
              <div class="guide-quota-desc">Non-Institutional Investors (apply above ₹2 lakhs)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="guide-quota-item">
              <div class="guide-quota-pct" style="color:#22c55e">35%</div>
              <div class="guide-quota-lbl">Retail</div>
              <div class="guide-quota-desc">Individual investors applying up to ₹2 lakhs. Minimum 1 lot via UPI/ASBA.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  // ── Tab management ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  const tabs = [
    { btn:'tabOngoing',  panel:'panelOngoing' },
    { btn:'tabUpcoming', panel:'panelUpcoming' },
    { btn:'tabListed',   panel:'panelListed' },
    { btn:'tabGuide',    panel:'panelGuide' },
  ];
  tabs.forEach(({ btn, panel }) => {
    document.getElementById(btn).addEventListener('click', () => {
      tabs.forEach(t => {
        document.getElementById(t.btn).classList.remove('active');
        document.getElementById(t.panel).style.display = 'none';
      });
      document.getElementById(btn).classList.add('active');
      document.getElementById(panel).style.display = 'block';
    });
  });

  // ── Render helpers ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  function fmt(v) { return v || '—'; }

  function renderIpoCard(ipo, type) {
    const statusColor = type === 'ongoing' ? '#22c55e' : type === 'upcoming' ? '#f59e0b' : '#7a8899';
    const statusLabel = type === 'ongoing' ? 'OPEN NOW' : type === 'upcoming' ? 'UPCOMING' : 'LISTED';
    return `
      <div class="ipo-card">
        <div class="ipo-card-header">
          <div>
            <div class="ipo-card-name">${fmt(ipo.company)}</div>
            ${ipo.symbol ? `<div class="ipo-card-sym">${ipo.symbol}</div>` : ''}
          </div>
          <span class="ipo-status-badge" style="background:${statusColor}22;color:${statusColor};border:1px solid ${statusColor}55">${statusLabel}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ipo-card-grid">
          ${type !== 'listed' ? `
            <div class="ipo-card-field">
              <div class="ipo-field-lbl">Open Date</div>
              <div class="ipo-field-val">${fmt(ipo.openDate)}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ipo-card-field">
              <div class="ipo-field-lbl">Close Date</div>
              <div class="ipo-field-val">${fmt(ipo.closeDate)}</div>
            </div>` : ''}
          ${ipo.listingDate ? `
            <div class="ipo-card-field">
              <div class="ipo-field-lbl">Listing Date</div>
              <div class="ipo-field-val">${fmt(ipo.listingDate)}</div>
            </div>` : ''}
          <div class="ipo-card-field">
            <div class="ipo-field-lbl">Issue Price</div>
            <div class="ipo-field-val">${ipo.priceMin && ipo.priceMax && ipo.priceMin !== ipo.priceMax ? `₹${ipo.priceMin} – ₹${ipo.priceMax}` : ipo.priceMin ? `₹${ipo.priceMin}` : '—'}</div>
          </div>
          ${ipo.lotSize ? `
            <div class="ipo-card-field">
              <div class="ipo-field-lbl">Lot Size</div>
              <div class="ipo-field-val">${fmt(ipo.lotSize)} shares</div>
            </div>` : ''}
          ${ipo.issueSize ? `
            <div class="ipo-card-field">
              <div class="ipo-field-lbl">Issue Size</div>
              <div class="ipo-field-val">${fmt(ipo.issueSize)}</div>
            </div>` : ''}
        </div>
      </div>`;
  }

  function renderEmpty(type) {
    const msg = {
      ongoing:  { icon:'📭', title:'No IPOs open right now', desc:'When an IPO subscription window is open, it will appear here. New IPOs are announced by NSE/BSE typically 5–7 days before opening.' },
      upcoming: { icon:'🗓️', title:'No upcoming IPOs announced', desc:'Companies typically announce IPO dates 10–15 days in advance. Check back regularly or follow NSE\'s official announcements.' },
      listed:   { icon:'📋', title:'No recent IPO data', desc:'Recently listed IPOs will appear here once data refreshes via GitHub Actions.' },
    };
    const m = msg[type];
    return `<div style="text-align:center;padding:48px 20px">
      <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:12px">${m.icon}</div>
      <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px">${m.title}</div>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);max-width:400px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.6">${m.desc}</div>
    </div>`;
  }

  // ── Load from JSON ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  async function loadIPOs() {
    try {
      const r    = await fetch('/data/ipo.json');
      const data = await r.json();

      // Ongoing
      const ongoingEl  = document.getElementById('ongoingContent');
      const ongoingLdr = document.getElementById('ongoingLoading');
      if (data.ongoing && data.ongoing.length) {
        ongoingEl.innerHTML = data.ongoing.map(i => renderIpoCard(i, 'ongoing')).join('');
      } else {
        ongoingEl.innerHTML = renderEmpty('ongoing');
      }
      ongoingLdr.style.display = 'none';
      ongoingEl.style.display  = 'block';

      // Upcoming
      const upcomingEl  = document.getElementById('upcomingContent');
      const upcomingLdr = document.getElementById('upcomingLoading');
      if (data.upcoming && data.upcoming.length) {
        upcomingEl.innerHTML = data.upcoming.map(i => renderIpoCard(i, 'upcoming')).join('');
      } else {
        upcomingEl.innerHTML = renderEmpty('upcoming');
      }
      upcomingLdr.style.display = 'none';
      upcomingEl.style.display  = 'block';

      // Listed
      const listedEl  = document.getElementById('listedContent');
      const listedLdr = document.getElementById('listedLoading');
      if (data.listed && data.listed.length) {
        listedEl.innerHTML = data.listed.map(i => renderIpoCard(i, 'listed')).join('');
      } else {
        listedEl.innerHTML = renderEmpty('listed');
      }
      listedLdr.style.display = 'none';
      listedEl.style.display  = 'block';

    } catch (err) {
      ['ongoingLoading','upcomingLoading','listedLoading'].forEach(id => {
        document.getElementById(id).innerHTML = `<div style="text-align:center;padding:32px;color:var(--text-muted)">Could not load IPO data — try refreshing.</div>`;
      });
    }
  }

  loadIPOs();
</script>

<style>
/* IPO Cards */
.ipo-card {
  background:var(--navy-2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px;
  padding:20px; margin-bottom:14px; transition:border-color 0.2s;
}
.ipo-card:hover { border-color:rgba(212,169,64,0.3); }
.ipo-card-header {
  display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}
.ipo-card-name { font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; }
.ipo-card-sym  { font-size:12px; color:var(--gold); font-weight:600; margin-top:2px; }
.ipo-status-badge {
  font-size:10px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:0.8px;
  padding:3px 10px; border-radius:20px; white-space:nowrap;
}
.ipo-card-grid {
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(130px, 1fr)); gap:12px;
}
.ipo-card-field { }
.ipo-field-lbl { font-size:10px; color:var(--text-muted); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:3px; }
.ipo-field-val { font-size:13px; color:var(--text); font-weight:600; }

/* Guide */
.ipo-guide { max-width:760px; }
.guide-section-title { font-size:17px; font-weight:700; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:20px; }
.guide-steps { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px; margin-bottom:28px; }
.guide-step  { display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:flex-start; }
.guide-step-num {
  flex-shrink:0; width:32px; height:32px; border-radius:50%;
  background:rgba(212,169,64,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(212,169,64,0.3);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-size:13px; font-weight:800; color:var(--gold);
}
.guide-step-title { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:4px; }
.guide-step-desc  { font-size:13px; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.6; }

.guide-tips-grid {
  display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:14px; margin-bottom:24px;
}
.guide-tip {
  background:var(--navy-2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px;
  padding:16px;
}
.guide-tip-icon  { font-size:22px; margin-bottom:8px; }
.guide-tip-title { font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:4px; }
.guide-tip-text  { font-size:12px; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.6; }

.guide-quota { background:var(--navy-2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:20px; }
.guide-quota-title { font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:16px; }
.guide-quota-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); gap:12px; }
.guide-quota-item { text-align:center; padding:14px 8px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-radius:8px; }
.guide-quota-pct  { font-size:28px; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:4px; }
.guide-quota-lbl  { font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:4px; }
.guide-quota-desc { font-size:11px; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.5; }

@media (max-width:640px) {
  .guide-tips-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .guide-quota-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
}
</style>
